Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:46.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}给我一些颤音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}奋起直追
